item.title: CVE-2018-15331|2024-09-16T16:33:06.373Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- big-ip%20%28aam%29
item.description: On BIG-IP AAM 13.0.0 or 12.1.0-12.1.3.7, the dcdb_convert utility used by BIG-IP AAM fails to drop group permissions when executing helper scripts, which could be used to leverage attacks against the BIG-IP system.
